defaultFinancial barriers:
default&#xa0;
defaultThese include: limited disposable income; rising/high entry fees; long-term membership requirements for gyms and leisure centres; cost of clothing and equipment. 
defaultIf we are to increase participation consideration must be given to a) the actual costs of participation and b) the way we market the sport and our products.
