defaultbarriers include: 
defaultlack of confidence and low self esteem/perceptions of ability/body image; perceptions of sport as male-dominated, unfeminine activity; peer pressure; lack of parental support; cultural restrictions; lack of positive role models; 
defaultcompetitive/aggressive/intimidating environments; 
defaultlack of friends/people to participate with. Suggested actions include: 
default&#xa0;
